KwaZulu-Natal Cooperative Governance and Traditional Affairs MEC Sipho Hlomuka eNCA JOHANNESBURG - KZN COGTA MEC Sipho Hlomuka has condemned the assassination of iNkosi Maxwell Nxumalo of Ladysmith. iNkosi Nxumalo was shot dead in the early hours of this morning. MEC Hlomuka has called on law enforcement agencies to apprehend those responsible. He says they have been actively engaged with safety issues raised by Amakhosi and has noted the work done by the law enforcement agencies to apprehend people responsible for attacks on amakhosi and izinduna.